narratives.question_text: What knowledge, skills, and insights did you develop by taking this course?
comments: Concepts of procedures in high energy astrophysics, broader view on astrophysical topics, and skills to analyze spectra.

narratives.question_text: What are the strengths and weaknesses of this course and how could it be improved?
comments: Powerpoints were filled with great information. The project was a good demonstration of how the ideas are actually applied to research. The organization of the course could be improved. Sometimes the powerpoints jumped around or were given in a weird order.
I particularly like the range of topics it covered; However, the course can be improved by better organizing the context and highlighting the important points of each topic.

narratives.question_text: Would you recommend this course to another student? Please explain.
comments: I will probably recommend the course to someone willing to explore his/her possibility in relative research, e.g. AGN, cosmic rays, etc.
